*Zgodan* mladić je išao ulicom. (The handsome young man was walking down the street.)

Njegova sestra je bila takođe *zgodna*. (His sister was also attractive.)

On je često bio u društvu *zgodnih* devojaka. (He was often in the company of attractive girls.)

Njegov stil oblačenja je bio savremeno *zgodan*. (His style of dressing was modern and attractive.)

Ona je uvek našla način da bude *zgodna*. (She always found ways to be attractive.)